spec_data.Name: mojo-keytool-maven-plugin
spec_data.Description:
A plugin that wraps the keytool program bundled with Java SDK.
It provides the capability to manipulate keys and keystores
with the goals "keytool:genkey" and "keytool:clean".
spec_data.Signature: RSA/SHA256, Thu 27 Jul 2017 11:25:00 AM EDT, Key ID f55e7430f5282ee4
spec_data.Summary: A plugin that wraps the keytool program and allows to manipulate keystores
